events.description_preview: OverviewExperience what happens when sacred sound touches your heart. Worries fly away. The weight l...
events.description_detail: OverviewExperience what happens when sacred sound touches your heart. Worries fly away. The weight lifts. Joy awakens.We had so much fun last month, we just had to come back to Cupertino for more Kirtan before we wrap up our California coastal tour! We can‚Äôt wait to see you again and if you missed it the first time, we‚Äôd love to meet you.Step into another worldWhere meditation meets celebration.We begin with a mantra and a melody, an invitation to let Yoga Sound do its work. Instead of battling your mind, you feel lighter, as if your whole being can breathe freely. Gradually, the kirtan carries you from deep calm to pure joy.Ride the wave of transcendental soundAs the kirtan builds, the energy swells like a rising wave. Some sit back and let it wash over them, others dive right in‚Äîsinging and dancing freely. Time seems to stand still and you feel fully present, knowing this is exactly where you‚Äôre meant to be.Why we share thisFor thousands of years, people have sung these mantras to uncover inner peace and fulfillment. The yoga sages call kirtan the easiest and most effective form of meditation. Why? Because these sacred sounds awaken the love and joy already there in our heart.Kirtan has changed our lives‚Äîthat‚Äôs why we share it. And in sharing, we‚Äôve seen how it brings people together across backgrounds and beliefs, creating a sense of unity the world needs now more than ever.What People Tell UsWe see it all the time‚Äîpeople who come as strangers leave as friends, those who arrive anxious leave calm, and hearts open."I didn't know I could feel this peaceful.""I've been meditating for years, but this was different.""Although I'd never heard the mantras before, they felt very familiar and comforting."Everyone is welcomeWhether you‚Äôve been to kirtan a hundred times or this is your first, just come as you are. Bring friends or make new ones here. This isn‚Äôt a performance‚Äîit‚Äôs something we create together, and every voice belongs.Don‚Äôt just hear about it‚Äîbe part of it.Read moreCategory: Spirituality, Unaffiliated

events.description_preview: OverviewLife can be so busy with no time to make new connections on your own. Start off as strangers...
events.description_detail: OverviewLife can be so busy with no time to make new connections on your own. Start off as strangers, then become friends over dinner!Everyone has something to bring to the table...literally.Our series groups together complete strangers for a fun night out over dinner. That's right, you sign up, and we book the restaurant. We know life can get busy. Don't do life alone and build your community with us, all the while supporting local businesses. We coordinate dinners in over 200 cities.This gathering isn't an official event with the restaurant but rather an outing based on a table reservation. The pin on the map is not the location, but a placeholder on Eventbrite as each week is held at a different location.Our feature on Fox 11 Los Angeles.Please see here for our coverage in Nashville Fox 17's Growing Nashville segment.Each evening is intended to be for 4-6 people maximum. Check out our feature in Eventbrite's 2025 TRNDS report about embracing the micro-event trend.How does it work?After you register, you'll be emailed an introduction message. If you don't get an email after five minutes of signing up, contact us with your registration at ermantourageimpact@gmail.com.*Your registration does not include your individual food and drink purchases. A paid ticket simply makes you more committed to actually showing up.*These outings are intended to help people make friends. These are not singles gatherings.*If we don't meet our minimum number of registrants for the evening you sign up, please be open to joining us on another evening! We will complete table reservations after we hit our minimum signups, so you may reach out to us before signing up for or after you sign up to see our progress with registrations for the evening.*If you sign up the day of the gathering and do not get a message from us in time, simply email ermantourageimpact@gmail.com, request a refund, or please be open to joining us on another evening.Our vision is simple: we take the no gimmicks approach to networking. No need for yet another app to take up space on your phone - just four walls and a roof and good food for people to connect :) We coordinate with you directly, human-to-human.If you have any more questions, please contact ermantourageimpact@gmail.com! Follow us on Instagram!Read moreCategory: Food & Drink, Food

events.description_detail: OverviewA transformative afternoon of singing, soul, and spiritYou are invited to join Lauren Arrow and special guest Rena Branson as they come together to create a magickal musical ritual that is sure to be soul stirring and spirit lifting. Backed by the Big Effin' Band, this will be a collaborative performance featuring you!In classic Big Effin' Style‚Ä¶..you are an important part of this show! Singing with all y'all is the point, despite whatever judgement you've placed on your voice (good/bad/etc)! We just want to sing with you. (Aaaaaaand if you feel abject terror around singing but just want to listen you are welcome too ‚ù§)Enjoy an afternoon of original music by Lauren and Rena, soulful covers, and heart melting wordless melodies to lose yourself in. She lives for the magic of group singing and knows her job is done when people cry, dance - or both (simultaneously?).
